         <div type="metricalScheme">
            <p>Ballata grande 10’z 6’y 6’y 10’z; 6’a 6’a 10’b, 6’a 6’a 10’b; 10’b 6’c 6’c 10’z (nella seconda strofa b = z).</p> 
